Keep in mind that this kind of programming is very advanced and should only be done by experienced programmers. If you're not sure what you're doing, you could easily make your system unstable or insecure. Also, manipulating the NDIS in ways that aren't documented by Microsoft could break compatibility with future versions of Windows.

